### =====================================================================
### ChargeInternet API  (base route: api/ChargeInternet/)
### =====================================================================
@host = http://localhost:5000
@apiKey = your-dev-api-key
@token =

### Pin - buy a charge pin
POST {{host}}/api/ChargeInternet/Pin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "amount": 20000,
  "simType": "HamrahAvval"
}

### Topup - direct top-up
POST {{host}}/api/ChargeInternet/Topup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "amount": 20000,
  "operatorId": "1",
  "chargeType": "normal",
  "phoneNumber": "09120000000"
}

### InternetList - available packages for an operator
POST {{host}}/api/ChargeInternet/InternetList
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "operatorId": "1"
}

### InternetReserve - reserve a package
POST {{host}}/api/ChargeInternet/InternetReserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "subscriber": "09120000000",
  "operatorId": "1",
  "packageId": "PKG-123",
  "amount": 50000,
  "device": "05",
  "bank": null
}

### GetStatus - by reference
POST {{host}}/api/ChargeInternet/GetStatus
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "reference": "REF-123456"
}

### GetBalance (no body required)
POST {{host}}/api/ChargeInternet/GetBalance

### Echo (health check, no body required)
POST {{host}}/api/ChargeInternet/Echo
